<Body><Title>意大利驻华大使强烈谴责昆明暴力恐怖袭击事件</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014年03月04日</ReportTime>
	<Content><Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">国际在线</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">消息</Denoter></Event>（记者 杨晓囡、向菲）：
<Event eid="e2"><Location lid="l2">中国云南省昆明市</Location>“<Time tid="t2" type="relTime">3・01</Time>”严重<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">暴力恐怖</Denoter>事件发生后</Event>，
<Event eid="e3"><Participant oid="o3" sid="s4,s5">意大利驻华大使白达宁</Participant><Time tid="t3" type="relTime">4日</Time>在接受<Denoter did="d3" type="operation">采访</Denoter>时</Event>，
<Event eid="e4">对<Object oid="o4">该事件</Object>表达了强烈的<Denoter did="d4" type="perception">谴责</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e5">并对<Participant oid="o5">中国人民和政府</Participant>表达了深切的<Denoter did="d5" type="perception">慰问</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e6" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s6">白达宁</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="statement">说</Denoter></Event>，“
<Event eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7,s10">我</Participant>要以大使的身份，对这起<Object oid="o7">恐怖袭击事件</Object>表示强烈<Denoter did="d7" type="perception">谴责</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
			<Sentence><Event eid="e8">这起<Denoter did="d8" type="emergency">恐怖袭击</Denoter>事件</Event>，
<Event eid="e9">对<Participant oid="o9">中国、对失去生命的遇难者及家人</Participant>，都造成了严重的<Denoter did="d9" type="operation">损害</Denoter>。</Event></Sentence>
			<Sentence>这是一起毫无意义的恐怖事件。</Sentence>
			<Sentence>借此机会，
我<Event eid="e10">要对<Participant oid="o10">中国人民，中国政府，特别是对遇难者的家属</Participant>，表示深切的<Denoter did="d10" type="perception">慰问</Denoter>。</Event></Sentence>
			<Sentence><Event eid="e11" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s11">我</Participant><Denoter did="d11" type="perception">认为</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e12" polarity="negative">没有任何<Object sid="s12">理由</Object>可以为这次恐怖袭击的<Object oid="o12">行为</Object><Denoter did="d12" type="statement">辩护</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e13" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d13" type="perception">希望</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">恐怖分子和其幕后恐怖集团</Participant>尽快<Denoter did="d14" type="operation">伏法</Denoter>。</Event>”</Sentence></Paragraph></Content>
